expfep
======

expfep is fep (front end processor) in terminal using [expect](https://core.tcl-lang.org/expect/)

requirement
===========

  -  [tcl](https://tcl.tk/)
  -  [expect](https://core.tcl-lang.org/expect/home)
  -  tput

starpack binary expfep-linux-x86_64 contains tcl and expect.

usage
=====

run tcl script

    $ tclsh expfep.vfs/main.tcl [-e command]

or run starpack binary file

    $ ./expfep-linux-x86_64 [-e command]

keybindigs
==========

always

    ^\	toggle fep on/off

fep on state

    M-1	hiragana
    M-2	katakana
    M-3	cangjie
    M-4	skk-jisyo

if has candidate

    ^G	cancel
    space	commit
    ^N	next cand
    ^P	previous cand
    ^F	next page
    ^B	previous page
    ^A	first cand
    ^E	last cand

configuration
=============

edit config.tcl

